---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Meals & Food Options | Jyoti Girls PG Osmanpura"
  description="Jyoti Girls PG does not bundle meals — we recommend the best local mess and tiffin options near Osmanpura so residents eat real home-cooked food, not institutional bulk cooking."
>

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section style="padding: 60px 0 40px; background: var(--color-bg-base);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Food near Jyoti Girls PG</span>
      <h1 class="section-heading" style="max-width:640px;">We don't bundle food — we recommend the best</h1>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Most hostels in Osmanpura charge ₹5,000 with meals included. The food is institutional, bulk-cooked, and most girls don't eat it. We keep your rent low and point you to the best home-cooked options in the neighbourhood — so you actually enjoy what you eat.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why we don't bundle meals -->
  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white); padding: 48px 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Our philosophy</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Forced mess = wasted money</h2>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; max-width: 860px;">

        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:10px;">❌</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:8px;">The bundled mess problem</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.6;">
            Nearby hostels charge ₹4,500–5,500 with meals included. The food is cooked in bulk for 50–100 people, tastes the same every day, and most girls stop eating it within a month — but keep paying for it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="border-color: var(--color-primary-light);">
          <div style="font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:10px;">✓</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:8px; color:var(--color-primary);">The Jyoti Girls PG way</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.6;">
            We keep rent honest at ₹2,999–₹5,000 and let you choose where you eat. We have personally vetted the best local mess and tiffin options nearby — real home-cooked food from local families at ₹60–80 per meal.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Recommended food options -->
  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-subtle); padding: 48px 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Our recommendations</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Where Jyoti Girls PG residents eat</h2>
      <p style="font-size:0.95rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom:32px; max-width:560px;">
        These are options we have personally tried and recommend to our residents. All are within 5 minutes' walk from the PG.
      </p>

      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:20px; max-width:960px;">

        <!-- Cafe Aveen's -->
        <div class="card">
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:12px;">
            <div style="width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--color-primary-pale); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:1.2rem; flex-shrink:0;">☕</div>
            <div>
              <p style="font-size:14px; font-weight:600; margin:0; color:var(--color-text-primary);">Cafe Aveen's</p>
              <p style="font-size:11px; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0;">Right next to the PG</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:12px;">
            The most convenient option — located right next to Jyoti Girls PG. Serves quick meals including Maggi, omelettes, biryani, sandwiches, and chai. Open from morning until late evening.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px;">
            <span class="badge badge-teal">Quick meals</span>
            <span class="badge badge-warm">Breakfast</span>
            <span class="badge badge-warm">Snacks</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Jyoti Mess -->
        <div class="card">
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:12px;">
            <div style="width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--color-cta-light); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:1.2rem; flex-shrink:0;">🍱</div>
            <div>
              <p style="font-size:14px; font-weight:600; margin:0; color:var(--color-text-primary);">Jyoti Mess</p>
              <p style="font-size:11px; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0;">3 min walk · Home-style thali</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:12px;">
            Family-run mess serving authentic home-style Maharashtrian thali — dal, sabzi, chapati, rice, and pickle. Monthly subscription available at approximately ₹1,800–2,200 for two meals daily.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px;">
            <span class="badge badge-teal">Lunch & dinner</span>
            <span class="badge badge-warm">Monthly plan</span>
            <span class="badge badge-teal">Home-cooked</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Home tiffin delivery -->
        <div class="card">
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:12px;">
            <div style="width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--color-primary-pale); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:1.2rem; flex-shrink:0;">🏠</div>
            <div>
              <p style="font-size:14px; font-weight:600; margin:0; color:var(--color-text-primary);">Home tiffin delivery</p>
              <p style="font-size:11px; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0;">Delivered to PG gate</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:12px;">
            Several local families near Osmanpura offer home tiffin delivery — fresh, seasonal, and genuinely home-cooked. We maintain a current list of trusted tiffin providers and share it with every new resident on arrival.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px;">
            <span class="badge badge-teal">Delivered to gate</span>
            <span class="badge badge-warm">₹60–80/meal</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Ask us CTA -->
      <div style="background: var(--color-primary-pale); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 20px 24px; margin-top: 28px; max-width: 560px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:14px;">
        <div>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--color-primary); margin:0 0 4px;">Want our current tiffin recommendations?</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0;">We update this list every semester. WhatsApp us and we'll share the best current options.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305?text=Hi%20Jyoti%20Girls%20PG%2C%20can%20you%20share%20tiffin%20and%20mess%20recommendations%20near%20the%20PG%3F" class="btn-primary" style="white-space:nowrap;">Ask on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What a typical food day looks like -->
  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white); padding: 48px 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">A typical day</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading">What most residents eat in a day</h2>
      <div style="max-width:640px;">

        <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <div style="width:80px; flex-shrink:0; font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--color-primary); padding-top:2px;">Morning</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.6;">Chai and poha or vada pav from Cafe Aveen's or Osmanpura road stalls before heading to college — ₹20–40, takes 5 minutes.</div>
        </div>

        <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <div style="width:80px; flex-shrink:0; font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--color-primary); padding-top:2px;">Lunch</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.6;">Most residents use the college canteen or a tiffin subscription for lunch. A full thali at Jyoti Mess or via tiffin delivery costs ₹60–80.</div>
        </div>

        <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <div style="width:80px; flex-shrink:0; font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--color-primary); padding-top:2px;">Evening</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.6;">Cafe Aveen's for Maggi, sandwiches, or chai after coaching or college. Quick, affordable, and right at the doorstep.</div>
        </div>

        <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; padding:14px 0;">
          <div style="width:80px; flex-shrink:0; font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--color-primary); padding-top:2px;">Dinner</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.6;">Tiffin delivery at the PG gate or Jyoti Mess — home-cooked dinner at ₹60–80. Monthly tiffin plan works out to approximately ₹1,800–2,000 for dinner only.</div>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin-top:16px; font-style:italic;">
          Estimated monthly food cost: ₹2,500–3,500 depending on choices — far less than the ₹1,500–2,000 premium hostels charge for bundled food you won't enjoy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Facilities section -->
  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-subtle); padding: 48px 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Included in your rent</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Facilities at Jyoti Girls PG</h2>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; max-width:860px;">

        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:8px;">⚡</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px;">24x7 power backup</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.83rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0; line-height:1.5;">Lights, fans, and Wi-Fi stay on during load shedding. No interruptions during exam season.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:8px;">📶</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px;">High-speed Wi-Fi</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.83rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0; line-height:1.5;">Reliable internet for online resources, assignment uploads, and video calls home.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:8px;">🧹</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px;">Daily housekeeping</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.83rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0; line-height:1.5;">Rooms and common areas cleaned daily. Washrooms maintained multiple times a day.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:8px;">💧</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px;">RO drinking water</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.83rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0; line-height:1.5;">Filtered RO water available 24x7 in common areas. No need to buy packaged water.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:8px;">👗</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px;">Laundry service</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.83rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0; line-height:1.5;">Regular laundry and ironing service available. Saves time during busy exam periods.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:8px;">🔒</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px;">Personal locker</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.83rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin:0; line-height:1.5;">Dedicated locker for valuables, documents, and electronics in every room.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-base); padding: 48px 0;">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center; max-width:520px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:12px;">Good food + safe stay = a productive year</h2>
      <p style="font-size:0.95rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom:24px;">
        Beds are limited. WhatsApp us to check availability and get our latest tiffin recommendations.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305?text=Hi%20Jyoti%20Girls%20PG%2C%20I%20want%20to%20check%20bed%20availability%20and%20get%20tiffin%20recommendations." class="btn-primary">WhatsApp us</a>
        <a href="/admissions-contact" class="btn-outline">View admissions</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
